WEBVTT

00:00:06.981 --> 00:00:13.404
THIS IS TAPE THREE OF THE INTERVIEW BEING CONDUCTED IN MELBOURNE, AUSTRALIA, WITH LEIBUSH LICHTENSTEIN, MARCH THE FIRST

00:00:13.461 --> 00:00:15.243
NINETEEN NINETY EIGHT

00:00:17.055 --> 00:00:20.829
⟨bay⟩ di ende fun di letste tashme, hostu geredt vegn di

00:00:20.937 --> 00:00:23.394
eyner vos hot

00:00:22.692 --> 00:00:24.679
an ukrainets?

00:00:23.620 --> 00:00:24.525
yo.

00:00:24.679 --> 00:00:26.853
der ukrainets hot ongehoybn

00:00:27.501 --> 00:00:28.924
ibertsufirn

00:00:28.924 --> 00:00:31.427
evakuirn, ir veyst vos heyst evakuirn?

00:00:32.023 --> 00:00:34.430
ibertsufirn mentshn, fardinen gelt.

00:00:35.871 --> 00:00:37.265
ikh hob gezen

00:00:38.217 --> 00:00:41.788
az undz vet men zeyer mies opshnaydn, oyb m'vet

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:45.686
m'vet zayn dortn in di pletser, in dem dorf

00:00:47.430 --> 00:00:48.504
mit im

00:00:48.780 --> 00:00:51.491
hot men bashlosn ibertsulozn im

00:00:51.548 --> 00:00:53.097
dem ukrainets mit di

00:00:53.097 --> 00:00:54.253
mit di ferd

00:00:54.253 --> 00:00:56.081
un undz zoln mir geyn loyt

00:00:56.087 --> 00:00:57.788
m'hot gehat an onvayzung

00:00:57.788 --> 00:00:58.967
KHARKOV.

00:01:00.188 --> 00:01:01.565
dort vet kumen

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:05.041
a transport ⟨fun⟩ vagener

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:07.101
m'vet undz dortn oyflodeven

00:01:07.275 --> 00:01:08.551
un forn

00:01:08.575 --> 00:01:10.644
oyf di rikhtung vu undz darf men.

00:01:12.169 --> 00:01:14.492
haklal, m'hot dortn gevart a tsayt.

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:16.651
m'iz aroysganen

00:01:16.911 --> 00:01:18.069
oyfn feld

00:01:20.404 --> 00:01:22.862
un m'hot, m'hot genumen a

00:01:22.986 --> 00:01:26.270
der ukrainer hot genumen a sheps, hot gekhapt a sheps

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:28.751
un m'hot dem sheps opgeshokhtn

00:01:29.078 --> 00:01:31.670
un arayngekumen, un arayngenumen tsu

00:01:31.963 --> 00:01:33.729
a goye, tsu a

00:01:33.820 --> 00:01:35.214
a ukrainke.

00:01:35.355 --> 00:01:37.976
m'hot dos gemakht in ordenung dos fleysh

00:01:37.976 --> 00:01:39.956
un zi hot dos opgebakn

00:01:40.013 --> 00:01:42.524
a halb far zikh, halb far ir.

00:01:42.524 --> 00:01:44.059
zi hot undz opgebakn

00:01:44.059 --> 00:01:45.255
a por broyt

00:01:45.396 --> 00:01:46.706
un m'iz geforn.

00:01:47.202 --> 00:01:48.326
⟨m'iz⟩ geforn

00:01:48.703 --> 00:01:52.004
shpeter hob ikh gezen az me ken nisht adurkhgeyn mit dem

00:01:52.332 --> 00:01:54.092
az ⟨me⟩ muz antloyfn

00:01:54.092 --> 00:01:55.650
iz men geforn biz

00:01:55.858 --> 00:01:58.062
biz KHARKOV zenen mir geforn

00:01:58.727 --> 00:02:01.775
hot men gemoldn az s'vet nisht kumen der transport.

00:02:02.473 --> 00:02:04.495
undz hot men gehat tsu forn

00:02:04.495 --> 00:02:06.196
NEMTSY POVOLZH'YA

00:02:07.788 --> 00:02:09.921
di onvayzung iz geven tsu forn

00:02:09.921 --> 00:02:11.580
NEMTSY POVOLZH'YA

00:02:11.923 --> 00:02:14.161
SARATOV, STALINGRAD.

00:02:16.547 --> 00:02:20.388
haklal, undz ze'mir geforn. m'hot im ibergelozt, dem ukrainets

00:02:20.428 --> 00:02:22.531
un undz ze'mir avekgeforn. m'hot zikh

00:02:23.162 --> 00:02:25.451
tsugeshlept biz dortn ahin.

00:02:25.508 --> 00:02:28.812
m'iz ahingekumen, un hot men undz arayngegebn in a KOLKHOZ

00:02:28.812 --> 00:02:30.514
un dortn hot men ongehoybn arbetn.

00:02:32.865 --> 00:02:34.867
m'hot undz gegebn a voynung.

00:02:35.262 --> 00:02:38.631
dortn zenen geven di daytshn, ⟨iz⟩ dortn geven, hot men zey aroyfgeshikt

00:02:38.839 --> 00:02:40.216
tif Sibir

00:02:40.932 --> 00:02:43.052
un m'hot undz gegebn zeyere voynungen.

00:02:42.720 --> 00:02:44.418
vu hot geheysn di dorf?

00:02:51.495 --> 00:02:55.421
tsi hot es geheysn ⟨ROLESH⟩ gedenk UNK s'hot geheysn dos dorf.

00:02:56.440 --> 00:02:58.560
gedenk shoyn gornisht vi s'hot geheysn.

00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:03.841
nu, lomir zogn Oyberdorf.

00:03:03.949 --> 00:03:05.816
Oyberdorf hot dos geheysn

00:03:06.430 --> 00:03:08.820
un dortn zenen mir geven in dem KOLKHOZ.

00:03:09.484 --> 00:03:11.317
vos far a arbet hostu getun?

00:03:11.762 --> 00:03:13.156
vos far an arbet?

00:03:13.635 --> 00:03:14.878
kh'hob gefirt

00:03:15.070 --> 00:03:17.156
s'ershte mol gefirt vaser

00:03:17.466 --> 00:03:18.658
in feser

00:03:19.103 --> 00:03:20.480
tsu di traktorn.

00:03:23.170 --> 00:03:25.408
traktorn hobn ibergearbet di felder.

00:03:25.954 --> 00:03:28.665
ikh hob gefirt vaser. shpeter hob ikh gefirt

00:03:29.768 --> 00:03:31.331
KHLEB ⟨OTSTAVKA⟩

00:03:32.198 --> 00:03:35.111
fun dem dorf hot men gegebn vos m'hot gedorfn ongebn f-

00:03:35.438 --> 00:03:37.102
far di regirung.

00:03:37.243 --> 00:03:39.312
yetveders dorf hot gehat

00:03:39.859 --> 00:03:41.034
a tsol

00:03:42.002 --> 00:03:44.443
vi heyst es, nu

00:03:44.719 --> 00:03:46.383
vifl me darf opgebn

00:03:46.609 --> 00:03:48.681
far militer, far di regirung

00:03:48.681 --> 00:03:51.311
un dos iberike hot men undz oysgetsolt far di arbet.

00:03:51.756 --> 00:03:53.153
hob ikh gefirt

00:03:53.153 --> 00:03:55.963
dos ge- di tvue

00:03:55.963 --> 00:03:58.173
hob ikh gefirt in di shtot arayn.

00:03:58.173 --> 00:03:59.676
dos ort hot geheysn

00:03:59.676 --> 00:04:00.677
KAMYSHIN.

00:04:02.353 --> 00:04:03.866
hob ikh opgefirt

00:04:04.345 --> 00:04:07.292
di tvue. s'hot geheysn KHLEB ⟨OTSTAVKA⟩

00:04:07.905 --> 00:04:10.045
un tsurik hob ikh gefirt vayter

00:04:10.045 --> 00:04:11.395
feser mit petrol

00:04:11.395 --> 00:04:12.624
tsu di traktorn.

00:04:13.204 --> 00:04:15.240
un dos iz geven ⟨same⟩ Rusland, yo?

00:04:15.043 --> 00:04:17.011
dos iz geven sh- dos iz gevezn

00:04:17.153 --> 00:04:19.290
NEMTSY POVOLZH'YA.

00:04:19.397 --> 00:04:20.926
dos iz gevezn

00:04:21.202 --> 00:04:24.150
s- SARATOV, STALINGRAD.

00:04:27.126 --> 00:04:32.267
vos hostu gehert fun, fun Poyln, fun di, fun di

00:04:32.138 --> 00:04:34.252
kh'hob gornisht gehert fun Poyln.

00:04:34.252 --> 00:04:36.080
absolut nisht gehert

00:04:37.032 --> 00:04:40.519
m'hot avekgeshikt etlekhene peklekh hot men avekgeshikt keyn Poyln

00:04:40.575 --> 00:04:41.784
produktn

00:04:42.229 --> 00:04:45.716
un m'hot nisht derhaltn keyn shum briv, keyn shum entfer nisht.

00:04:46.127 --> 00:04:49.057
tsi zey hobn yo derhaltn tsi nisht derhaltn

00:04:49.215 --> 00:04:50.761
m'hot gornisht gevust.

00:04:51.257 --> 00:04:53.124
m'hot geshikt tsu ir foter

00:04:53.350 --> 00:04:54.998
tsu mayn froy's foter

00:04:55.189 --> 00:04:57.310
hot men geshikt peklekh.

00:04:59.053 --> 00:05:02.740
un dos iz geven. m'hot geshikt. tsi es iz ongekumen tsi nisht veyst men nisht.

00:05:04.555 --> 00:05:06.523
vi hostu zikh gefilt vegn dem?

00:05:07.575 --> 00:05:08.801
vegn vos?

00:05:08.638 --> 00:05:10.758
vegn vos host gornisht gehert derfun.

00:05:10.579 --> 00:05:13.644
nu, vos hob ikh zikh gekent filn? koydem kol bin ikh geven

00:05:13.684 --> 00:05:15.030
m'iz geven yung.

00:05:15.030 --> 00:05:16.715
m'hot nisht getrakht fun dem.

00:05:17.177 --> 00:05:18.825
vos hot men gekent tun?

00:05:19.270 --> 00:05:21.002
shrayen tsun himl?

00:05:21.042 --> 00:05:22.824
vos vet undz helfn dos do?

00:05:24.670 --> 00:05:26.588
vos hobn mir gekent tun? gornisht.

00:05:27.285 --> 00:05:29.186
un di gezunt iz geven?

00:05:29.142 --> 00:05:31.633
yo. m'iz geven yung, m'iz geven gezunt.

00:05:33.580 --> 00:05:35.616
m'hot gegesn tsu di zet.

00:05:36.330 --> 00:05:38.433
di froy hot gebakn broyt

00:05:39.098 --> 00:05:41.623
un vi azoy dos lebn hot oysgezen

00:05:42.709 --> 00:05:44.981
iz azoy. azoy vi ikh hob gefirt

00:05:45.409 --> 00:05:48.710
di KHLEB ⟨OTSTAVKA⟩ far di regirung fun dorf

00:05:49.257 --> 00:05:50.938
hot men dem ⟨magaziner⟩

00:05:51.315 --> 00:05:53.435
vos hot gehaltn di shpaykhlers

00:05:53.577 --> 00:05:54.696
hot er gezogt

00:05:54.696 --> 00:05:56.271
"nem mit nokh a zekele"

00:05:56.968 --> 00:05:58.700
⟨vet zayn far dayne tsvek⟩

00:05:58.700 --> 00:05:59.729
⟨un far mir⟩.

00:06:01.778 --> 00:06:03.274
bin ahingeforn

00:06:03.415 --> 00:06:05.588
hob ikh gehat bazunder a zekele

00:06:05.588 --> 00:06:07.846
hot men mikh shoyn ongevart oyfn veg

00:06:08.595 --> 00:06:10.861
un dos farkoyft, hot er mir gezogt

00:06:10.861 --> 00:06:12.262
"zolst nisht aheymbrengen

00:06:12.262 --> 00:06:13.874
keyn eyn UNK nisht.

00:06:13.874 --> 00:06:16.504
breng aheym fleysh, breng aheym puter

00:06:18.248 --> 00:06:21.397
un breng aheym a fleshl vodke, vet men hobn tsu esn tsu trinken"

00:06:22.230 --> 00:06:23.045
un az-

00:06:23.045 --> 00:06:24.688
un azoy hob ikh getun.

00:06:28.221 --> 00:06:31.674
bist adurkhgekumen mit di, mit di rusn?

00:06:31.630 --> 00:06:33.750
yo, yo, yo. yo.

00:06:33.874 --> 00:06:34.644
yo.

00:06:39.848 --> 00:06:41.850
vi lang hostu gearbet azoy?

00:06:42.463 --> 00:06:44.077
vi lang ikh hob gearbet

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.731
dos iz gevezn

00:06:46.176 --> 00:06:50.996
ende tsvey un fertsik, onheyb dray un fertsik. nokh dem hot men mikh vayter mobilizirt

00:06:53.263 --> 00:06:54.573
un

00:06:55.677 --> 00:06:57.139
m'hot vayter

00:06:57.145 --> 00:06:58.303
gearbet.

00:06:58.815 --> 00:07:00.986
m'hot geboyt a ban linye.

00:07:01.903 --> 00:07:03.840
SARATOV STALINGRAD.

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:05.148
a geshikhte

00:07:05.148 --> 00:07:09.490
fun hundert un akhtsik kilometer a leng, a ban linye hot men ge-

00:07:10.122 --> 00:07:11.162
geboyt

00:07:11.252 --> 00:07:13.676
alts mit di hent gearbet. gegrobn

00:07:14.982 --> 00:07:16.573
alts gemakht mit di hent.

00:07:16.573 --> 00:07:18.620
dos iz geven a lange tsayt

00:07:19.082 --> 00:07:20.358
oyf azoy fil

00:07:20.668 --> 00:07:21.759
biz

00:07:22.677 --> 00:07:25.185
kh'hob gezen ikh ken shoyn vayter nisht oyshaltn

00:07:26.136 --> 00:07:27.530
hob ikh genumen

00:07:28.313 --> 00:07:30.028
di fis, bin antlofn.

00:07:30.878 --> 00:07:33.740
bin antlofn, ikh bin geforn mit di froy oyf Ukraine.

00:07:34.219 --> 00:07:35.866
un dos iz geven biz di ende

00:07:36.126 --> 00:07:38.044
biz tsun aheymforn keyn Poyln.

00:07:40.260 --> 00:07:42.431
vos iz forgekumen

00:07:42.522 --> 00:07:44.231
vegn di milkhome? d-

00:07:44.231 --> 00:07:49.063
d- d- d- daytshn hostu gezen in, ven du bist geven in STALINGRAD dortn?

00:07:48.985 --> 00:07:50.312
ikh hob nisht gezen.

00:07:50.098 --> 00:07:51.594
UNK. host gehert?

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:52.691
gehert hot men.

00:07:52.663 --> 00:07:53.990
d- di biksn?

00:07:52.697 --> 00:07:53.993
m'hot gehert

00:07:53.993 --> 00:07:56.319
m'hot gehert di bombardirung.

00:07:56.393 --> 00:07:58.024
m'hot gehert

00:07:58.435 --> 00:08:01.365
di gefalene. s'iz geven azoy fil gefalene

00:08:01.590 --> 00:08:03.254
az ⟨s'iz⟩ geven a shekht hoyz.

00:08:05.168 --> 00:08:06.630
vi hostu zey gezen?

00:08:05.202 --> 00:08:06.647
UNK

00:08:06.990 --> 00:08:10.500
 m'hot gehert vegn dem. eyner dem andern hot dertseylt v-

00:08:08.762 --> 00:08:09.684
yo

00:08:10.500 --> 00:08:13.580
vos iz geven? televizye? vos iz geven? s'iz gornisht geven.

00:08:13.580 --> 00:08:15.219
m'hot gehert, s'iz geven a

00:08:16.137 --> 00:08:19.084
a UNK iz gevezn, un az- dos hot men gehert.

00:08:20.035 --> 00:08:21.331
oyfgehongen oyf di v-

00:08:21.331 --> 00:08:23.590
iz geven a, vi heyst dos, a SLUKHAVKA

00:08:24.709 --> 00:08:26.407
azoy vi a telefon hert

00:08:26.970 --> 00:08:30.069
aza lomp un, un zey hobn ibergegebn.

00:08:30.227 --> 00:08:31.537
di UNK

00:08:31.898 --> 00:08:34.288
vu zey zenen ongefaln. m'hot zikh geharget di, mit di

00:08:34.288 --> 00:08:36.808
iber yetvedn hoyz hot men zikh geharget dortn.

00:08:37.703 --> 00:08:40.796
m'hot gehert vifl gefalene. m'hot gehert vi azoy

00:08:40.796 --> 00:08:43.839
di shlakht iz tsugegangen, un dos iz gevezn.

00:08:47.423 --> 00:08:47.909
m-

00:08:47.909 --> 00:08:51.872
bist, iz, far vos bistu tsurikgeforn keyn UKRAINE?

00:08:52.738 --> 00:08:54.335
vu hob ikh gezolt forn?

00:08:54.510 --> 00:08:56.647
kh'hob nisht gehat keyn ander plats tsu forn.

00:08:57.210 --> 00:08:59.262
dortn dem plats hob ikh shoyn gekent

00:09:01.345 --> 00:09:02.908
un dortn bin ikh geforn.

00:09:02.982 --> 00:09:09.220
hos- host nisht getrakht az, az s'kent rotn di daytshn, zol, zol zayn?

00:09:09.276 --> 00:09:11.306
neyn. dos iz shoyn gevezn

00:09:11.306 --> 00:09:13.643
ven zey hobn shoyn gehat tsurikgeyogt di daytshn.

00:09:12.833 --> 00:09:13.643
ah

00:09:13.643 --> 00:09:16.099
dos iz shoyn geven in di tsayt. dos iz shoyn geven

00:09:16.099 --> 00:09:17.978
in fir un fertsikstn yor.

00:09:19.063 --> 00:09:21.267
demolt iz nisht geven kaza sekone.

00:09:22.624 --> 00:09:26.516
un vos far a arbet hostu getun in, in, ven ⟨bist⟩ tsurikgekumen?

00:09:26.809 --> 00:09:28.203
keyn Ukraine?

00:09:27.433 --> 00:09:28.186
yo.

00:09:29.307 --> 00:09:32.206
s'iz UNK geven an arbet? s'iz geven vu tsu voynen? koym

00:09:32.206 --> 00:09:34.903
koym hot zikh arayngepakt in a tsimerl

00:09:34.960 --> 00:09:36.965
vu es hobn gevoynt fir mishpokhes

00:09:36.965 --> 00:09:38.565
aza koridor vi do.

00:09:40.866 --> 00:09:42.972
dort hot men geveynt, nisht gevoynt.

00:09:42.972 --> 00:09:43.880
geveynt.

00:09:44.106 --> 00:09:45.888
nu, vi azoy hot men gelebt?

00:09:46.063 --> 00:09:48.099
m'iz aroysgan oyfn TOLCHOK.

00:09:48.713 --> 00:09:49.989
m'hot gehandlt.

00:09:51.615 --> 00:09:54.303
gekumen di, di v- invalidn

00:09:54.303 --> 00:09:56.098
un zey hobn gebrengt skhoyre

00:09:56.678 --> 00:09:58.224
khaki skhoyre

00:09:58.922 --> 00:10:02.105
un m'hot gekoyft bay zey dos, UNK me zol oysgeyn oyfn mark

00:10:02.365 --> 00:10:03.894
un m'hot dos farkoyft.

00:10:05.503 --> 00:10:07.306
dos iz geven m'hot zikh oysgehaltn.

00:10:07.306 --> 00:10:08.434
azoy lang

00:10:08.608 --> 00:10:11.167
biz s'iz geven dortn a poylishe organizatsye

00:10:13.300 --> 00:10:16.331
ZWIAZEK hot dos geheysn POLSKICH PATRIOTOW

00:10:17.788 --> 00:10:19.818
un dortn hot men orga- organizirt

00:10:19.818 --> 00:10:20.957
grupes

00:10:20.957 --> 00:10:23.081
ver es vil aheymforn keyn Poyln.

00:10:23.357 --> 00:10:26.658
un dortn hot men zikh farshribn aheymtsuforn, iz men geforn keyn Poyln.

00:10:27.255 --> 00:10:29.831
dos iz geven shoyn finef un fertsikstn yor.

00:10:29.736 --> 00:10:31.164
tsurik tsu PSHEDBUZH?

00:10:30.968 --> 00:10:32.835
neyn, neyn, neyn, neyn.

00:10:33.904 --> 00:10:36.446
tsurik k- zenen mir geforn, m'iz geforn

00:10:36.840 --> 00:10:40.833
oyf farnumene gebitn fun DEUTSCHLAND

00:10:41.245 --> 00:10:42.893
vayl

00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:46.352
Poyln hot gekrign a teyl

00:10:47.269 --> 00:10:48.528
ZACHODNIA

00:10:49.412 --> 00:10:51.026
vu s'iz geven DEUTSCHLAND

00:10:51.083 --> 00:10:52.545
WROCLAW

00:10:53.614 --> 00:10:55.599
LEGNICA

00:10:55.842 --> 00:10:58.266
dortn di groy- a por groyse shtet

00:10:58.339 --> 00:11:00.273
dortn bin ikh ahingeforn

00:11:00.769 --> 00:11:02.689
un m'hot mir gegebn a voynung

00:11:02.689 --> 00:11:04.678
m'hot aroysgeshikt vayter di DEUTSCHEN.

00:11:05.157 --> 00:11:07.035
keyn DEUTSCHLAND zenen zey avekgeforn

00:11:07.035 --> 00:11:08.981
un dortn hob ikh genumen a voynung

00:11:09.021 --> 00:11:11.709
un dort hot men zikh oysgehaltn, vayter gehandlt.

00:11:11.603 --> 00:11:12.711
in WROCLAW?

00:11:12.970 --> 00:11:15.023
nisht in WR- DZIERZONIOW.

00:11:15.450 --> 00:11:16.422
DZIERZONIOW.

00:11:16.227 --> 00:11:17.740
nisht vayt fun WROCLAW?

00:11:17.239 --> 00:11:18.853
nisht vayt fun WROCLAW.

00:11:19.585 --> 00:11:22.312
un dortn hot men gevoynt a halb yor.

00:11:23.010 --> 00:11:24.911
m'hot gemakht a bisele gelt

00:11:25.288 --> 00:11:27.442
m'iz arayngeforn keyn tsentral Poyln.

00:11:27.499 --> 00:11:28.556
keyn Lodzh.

00:11:31.077 --> 00:11:33.653
vos far a arbet hostu getun in

00:11:35.008 --> 00:11:35.829
vu?

00:11:35.464 --> 00:11:39.339
in Poyln, in di, di por, por khadoshim ven bist geven dort?

00:11:39.042 --> 00:11:42.039
ikh bin nisht geven keyn por khadoshim. geven elef yor in Poyln.

00:11:41.792 --> 00:11:45.178
ne- f- far, farn araynkumen tsurik in Lodzh.

00:11:44.239 --> 00:11:45.898
 m'hot gehandlt.

00:11:45.758 --> 00:11:46.511
yo.

00:11:45.898 --> 00:11:47.712
vos iz, vos iz geven der handl?

00:11:47.712 --> 00:11:49.906
s'ershte bin ikh arayngan arbetn in a shop

00:11:49.906 --> 00:11:51.169
fun shnayderay

00:11:51.613 --> 00:11:52.923
mikh avekgezetst

00:11:52.923 --> 00:11:54.243
neyen hoyzns

00:11:54.243 --> 00:11:55.523
bashtelte hoyzns

00:11:55.523 --> 00:11:56.673
un kostyumen.

00:11:57.891 --> 00:12:00.605
in dem iz arayngekumen a DEUTSCH

00:12:00.605 --> 00:12:01.935
iz arayngekumen

00:12:02.312 --> 00:12:03.943
mit a kupon skhoyre

00:12:04.118 --> 00:12:05.681
dort in dem shop arayn

00:12:06.852 --> 00:12:09.293
un gevolt hobn zeks toyznt

00:12:10.243 --> 00:12:12.565
poylish gelt, zeks toyznt zlotes.

00:12:16.707 --> 00:12:19.384
⟨alzoy⟩, zey hobn nisht gevolt batsoln.

00:12:19.525 --> 00:12:21.949
di geshefts layt hobn nisht gevolt tsoln.

00:12:22.950 --> 00:12:25.002
bin ikh gegebn a gey aroys

00:12:25.549 --> 00:12:28.445
un ikh hob im gefregt, "gib mir" zog ikh "di adres

00:12:28.890 --> 00:12:30.436
vu du gefinst dikh"

00:12:30.561 --> 00:12:33.103
hot er mir gegebn di adres vu er gefint zikh

00:12:33.261 --> 00:12:35.060
bin ikh geganen mit di froy

00:12:36.400 --> 00:12:38.436
un ikh hob im shnel batsolt

00:12:38.728 --> 00:12:40.274
di zeks toyznt

00:12:41.665 --> 00:12:44.494
un ikh hob nisht gedronzhet ontsukukn dem kupon

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:47.041
hot men di froy farkoyft

00:12:47.368 --> 00:12:48.897
un genumen tsvelef

00:12:51.047 --> 00:12:53.420
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu handlen mit di DEUTSCHEN

00:12:53.848 --> 00:12:55.060
vayl far vos?

00:12:55.060 --> 00:12:56.790
zey hobn gehat rabirt

00:12:56.790 --> 00:12:57.791
bay yidn

00:12:58.506 --> 00:12:59.597
gekoyft

00:12:59.603 --> 00:13:01.683
⟨azelkhene⟩ tishtekher, gekoyft

00:13:01.683 --> 00:13:02.988
sheyne

00:13:03.636 --> 00:13:06.448
⟨Lublin⟩ tishtekher. m'hot gekoyft

00:13:06.572 --> 00:13:08.186
UNK

00:13:09.222 --> 00:13:10.481
mashinen

00:13:10.774 --> 00:13:14.517
un s'zenen gekumen fun tsentral Poyln, fun Varshe, fun Lodzh

00:13:14.517 --> 00:13:15.848
fun KRAKOW

00:13:15.921 --> 00:13:18.626
zey hobn undz, zey hobn dos opgekoyft bay undz.

00:13:18.626 --> 00:13:19.993
iz men dort gevezn

00:13:19.993 --> 00:13:21.365
a halb yor

00:13:21.456 --> 00:13:24.912
azoy ikh hob shoyn gepakt dem DEUTSCH, hot men ongevizn

00:13:24.912 --> 00:13:27.305
dos ort dortn fun di DEUTSCHEN

00:13:27.413 --> 00:13:30.731
hob ikh shoyn opgelozt dem shop vos ikh hob gearbet

00:13:31.075 --> 00:13:32.031
un

00:13:32.543 --> 00:13:34.461
⟨m'vet aleynt⟩ vern balebatim.

00:13:34.483 --> 00:13:38.172
un di froy iz geganen, dort opgekoyft bay di DEUTSCHEN hot zi opgekoyft

00:13:38.179 --> 00:13:39.337
gantse pek.

00:13:41.571 --> 00:13:43.252
hot opgekoyft

00:13:43.444 --> 00:13:46.070
a T.V., zi hot opgekoyft radyos

00:13:46.178 --> 00:13:48.129
mashinen, tepekher

00:13:48.388 --> 00:13:51.026
zenen gekumen fun ts- fun tsentral Poyln

00:13:51.026 --> 00:13:53.259
un zey hobn bar undz dos alts opgekoyft.

00:13:53.535 --> 00:13:55.995
zenen mir dort geven a knap halb yor

00:13:55.995 --> 00:13:57.815
hot men gemakht a bisl gelt.

00:13:57.872 --> 00:13:59.621
m'iz arayngeforn keyn Lodzh.

00:14:00.758 --> 00:14:02.307
in Lodzh hot men getrofn

00:14:02.307 --> 00:14:03.451
mishpokhe

00:14:03.897 --> 00:14:05.747
vos zenen geven in di lagern

00:14:05.820 --> 00:14:08.412
hobn zey undz dertseylt di gantse historye

00:14:08.419 --> 00:14:09.915
vos hot pasirt

00:14:09.955 --> 00:14:11.501
mit mayn vayb's eltern

00:14:12.250 --> 00:14:13.858
damolt ⟨hot⟩ men gevoyr gevorn.

00:14:13.858 --> 00:14:16.819
bin arayngeforn keyn Pshedbuzh. di froy mayne iz geforn

00:14:16.819 --> 00:14:18.116
keyn Pshedbuzh.

00:14:18.139 --> 00:14:20.613
zi hot in Pshedbuzh keynem nisht getrofn.

00:14:22.628 --> 00:14:24.278
keyner fun di mishpokhe

00:14:24.278 --> 00:14:25.811
nisht geven keyn shum lebedike.

00:14:26.728 --> 00:14:27.987
dos iz gevezn

00:14:28.247 --> 00:14:29.855
onheyb

00:14:29.855 --> 00:14:31.172
dos iz gevezn

00:14:31.172 --> 00:14:33.084
in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

00:14:36.853 --> 00:14:38.686
un dos iz geven di ende.

00:14:38.828 --> 00:14:41.818
demolt hot men gevoynt in Lodzh bay elef

00:14:41.818 --> 00:14:43.748
beerekh elef yor.

00:14:44.667 --> 00:14:48.255
nokh dem hot men gezen me ken nisht farblaybn in Lodzh.

00:14:48.987 --> 00:14:50.449
es forn aroys

00:14:50.657 --> 00:14:52.186
kimat ale yidn

00:14:53.087 --> 00:14:56.000
trakht ikh mir "ale zenen naronim, vel ikh ⟨oykh firn⟩ a"

00:14:56.479 --> 00:14:58.059
zenen mir oykh geforn.

00:14:58.420 --> 00:14:59.679
ikh bin arayngekumen

00:15:00.090 --> 00:15:01.451
keyn TEL AVIV

00:15:02.318 --> 00:15:04.354
⟨zenen mir⟩ arayngekumen goldene mentshn.

00:15:05.929 --> 00:15:08.302
kh'hob gehat a bisl gelt, hob ikh gekoyft a shtub

00:15:08.916 --> 00:15:10.142
in RAMAT GAN.

00:15:11.076 --> 00:15:12.858
keyn arbet hot men nisht gehat.

00:15:13.641 --> 00:15:15.238
s'iz nisht geven ⟨tsurik⟩ keyn arbet.

00:15:15.430 --> 00:15:17.398
s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer troyerik.

00:15:18.737 --> 00:15:20.283
bin ikh ganen in BEER SHEVA.

00:15:21.488 --> 00:15:22.359
horkht.

00:15:23.563 --> 00:15:25.261
bin ganen in BEER SHEVA arayn.

00:15:25.487 --> 00:15:27.489
ikh hob farkoyft dos voynung.

00:15:27.698 --> 00:15:28.941
kh'hob mir gemakht

00:15:28.947 --> 00:15:32.130
ayngekoyft ⟨SOLELOT⟩. veyst vos heyst ⟨SOLELOT⟩ tsi nisht?

00:15:32.575 --> 00:15:34.779
vu me ma- vu me shtelt arayn hiner

00:15:35.308 --> 00:15:37.614
⟨hobn⟩ oyfgevaksn, hob gekoyft

00:15:37.975 --> 00:15:40.247
di EFROCHIM, kleyne hinerlekh

00:15:40.911 --> 00:15:44.499
un kh'hob dos oysgevaremt. kh'hob gemakht fun dem oyfes

00:15:45.315 --> 00:15:47.536
un m'hot dos farkoyft oyf fleysh.

00:15:49.737 --> 00:15:50.844
RAMAT GAN.

00:15:50.901 --> 00:15:52.464
veyst vu RAMAT GAN iz?

00:15:52.774 --> 00:15:55.198
NETN- NETANYA, nisht RAMA- NETANYA.

00:15:55.710 --> 00:15:58.471
zenen mir arayngeforn. m'hot dort farkoyft di oyfes.

00:15:58.478 --> 00:16:01.678
zey hobn farkoyft di oyfes, di TNUVA.

00:16:01.785 --> 00:16:04.664
di TNUVA hot farkoyft oyf undzer kheshbn.

00:16:04.806 --> 00:16:08.279
zey zenen geven di balebatim. undz ze'mir geven di arbetorer

00:16:08.279 --> 00:16:10.321
un zey zenen geven di balebatim.

00:16:10.321 --> 00:16:13.940
s'iz gekumen a zaytiker mentsh, hot er gegebn a fuftsik a funt

00:16:13.940 --> 00:16:16.690
hobn zey farkoyft mayns a kestl oyfes

00:16:16.690 --> 00:16:19.530
far dem prayz. zey hobn gemakht dem prayz.

00:16:19.530 --> 00:16:21.391
az azoy, vifl m'hot nisht gek-

00:16:21.391 --> 00:16:23.509
geleyzt, hot men alts tsugeleygt.

00:16:23.509 --> 00:16:25.281
azoy koym kh'hob gezen

00:16:25.281 --> 00:16:27.193
kh'ken shoyn mer nisht oyshaltn

00:16:27.587 --> 00:16:30.956
bin ikh arayngan arbetn in a kibuts, UNK PARDES.

00:16:31.975 --> 00:16:33.758
kh'hob gearbet in PARDES

00:16:36.582 --> 00:16:39.208
un di froy iz geforn keyn TEL AVIV.

00:16:39.754 --> 00:16:43.016
zi hot UNK, hot zikh ayngedungen dortn oyf a plats.

00:16:43.016 --> 00:16:45.553
zi hot ongehoybn tsu neyen kinder kleydelekh.

00:16:45.913 --> 00:16:48.252
un zi hot dos farkoyft oyfn SHUK HAKARMEL.

00:16:48.310 --> 00:16:49.215
UNK

00:16:49.913 --> 00:16:51.023
nokh dem

00:16:51.023 --> 00:16:53.568
vi di froy iz shoyn arayngeforn keyn TEL AVIV

00:16:54.402 --> 00:16:57.146
hob ikh likvidirt dem kibuts

00:16:57.658 --> 00:17:00.262
hob oyfgehert tsu arbetn in dem ki- kibuts

00:17:00.262 --> 00:17:04.014
un ikh bin arayngeforn keyn TEL AVIV. m'hot zikh ayngedungen bay a TEIMANER

00:17:04.746 --> 00:17:06.798
un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu arbetn

00:17:06.990 --> 00:17:08.536
eksport arbet.

00:17:09.943 --> 00:17:11.675
bay ⟨eynem, bay an importirer⟩

00:17:11.952 --> 00:17:13.279
un demolt

00:17:13.436 --> 00:17:15.877
hot men ersht ongehoybn oyftsuheybn dem kop.

00:17:19.073 --> 00:17:22.206
farn avekforn fun, fun Lodzh

00:17:22.109 --> 00:17:22.845
yo

00:17:23.493 --> 00:17:25.191
keyn IS- keyn ISRAEL.

00:17:23.663 --> 00:17:28.114
host, host, yo, vos, vos iz geven di, di, di la-

00:17:28.114 --> 00:17:30.333
tsushtand tsvishn di, di

00:17:30.333 --> 00:17:32.077
polyakn un di yidn dortn?

00:17:33.096 --> 00:17:37.342
veyst nisht vos di shtimung iz gevezn? ⟨dem⟩ shtimung iz gevezn a shlekhte.

00:17:37.382 --> 00:17:39.266
yidn hobn ongehoybn tsu forn.

00:17:40.369 --> 00:17:43.366
iz, hot zikh gemakht antisemitishkeyt

00:17:43.390 --> 00:17:45.274
az yidn zoln forn.

00:17:46.090 --> 00:17:46.804
zey hobn

00:17:46.804 --> 00:17:49.695
zey hobn tsugefirt azoy az yidn zoln avekforn

00:17:50.157 --> 00:17:53.340
zoln blaybn aleynt on a yidn. zey hobn undz nisht gedorfn.

00:17:54.561 --> 00:17:57.305
host bamerkt epes,

00:17:56.502 --> 00:17:58.279
zikher hot men bamerkt.

00:17:57.379 --> 00:17:58.166
yo

00:17:58.279 --> 00:18:00.008
vayl m'hot geflegt di ershte tsayt

00:18:00.008 --> 00:18:02.809
hob ikh geflegt shteyn oyf a, oyf a bazar

00:18:02.809 --> 00:18:03.889
oyf a mark

00:18:03.889 --> 00:18:05.439
hoyzn farkoyfn

00:18:05.547 --> 00:18:07.397
zenen tsugekumen antisemitn

00:18:07.825 --> 00:18:10.671
un zey hobn zikh gevorfn, geshpign oyf undz.

00:18:11.554 --> 00:18:13.066
kh'hob gezen me ken nisht.

00:18:13.090 --> 00:18:15.803
ikh hob likvidirt. shpeter hob ikh gearbet in di heym.

00:18:15.803 --> 00:18:17.336
kh'hob aroysgegebn arbet

00:18:17.443 --> 00:18:20.002
un ikh hob gearbet mit, mit sokhrim

00:18:20.548 --> 00:18:21.959
CUSTOMERS

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:25.318
azoy in Poyln, kh'hob zikh an eytse gegebn shpeter

00:18:25.662 --> 00:18:27.765
azoy lang ikh hob gezen az

00:18:27.872 --> 00:18:31.173
me ken vayter nisht arbetn dortn, vayl alts iz gevezn

00:18:31.247 --> 00:18:32.388
oyf treyf.

00:18:33.036 --> 00:18:34.577
m'hot nisht gekrign

00:18:34.577 --> 00:18:36.720
tsugeteylt keyn skhoyre

00:18:36.720 --> 00:18:38.711
me zol kenen hobn an INVOICE

00:18:38.711 --> 00:18:40.804
me zol hobn vos oyftsuvayzn

00:18:40.804 --> 00:18:44.927
nor m'hot gemuzt koyfn umlegale skhoyre oyfn mark

00:18:45.844 --> 00:18:47.022
vos di

00:18:47.022 --> 00:18:49.433
froyen hobn genumen in di SHOPS

00:18:49.540 --> 00:18:50.743
in di magazinen

00:18:50.743 --> 00:18:52.942
tsu dray meter, tsu zeks meter

00:18:52.999 --> 00:18:55.372
un dos hobn zey farkoyft oyf di bazarn

00:18:55.918 --> 00:18:57.616
⟨vu⟩ mayn froy iz geforn

00:18:58.011 --> 00:19:00.738
oyfn bazar. zi hot dos oyfgekoyft, arayngeleygt

00:19:00.846 --> 00:19:02.488
tsu eyne tsu a froy

00:19:02.488 --> 00:19:06.107
un farnakht hot zi dos aheymgefirt, un dos hob ikh geshnitn di skhoyre

00:19:06.107 --> 00:19:07.336
un ikh hob farkoyft

00:19:07.427 --> 00:19:09.564
un hot men gekent ekzistirn azoy.

00:19:09.790 --> 00:19:12.366
dos muz dokh zayn epes hent mit fis.

00:19:13.080 --> 00:19:14.984
m'hot dokh ongegebn epes a barikht

00:19:14.984 --> 00:19:16.722
fun vanet me nemt di skhoyre

00:19:16.722 --> 00:19:18.002
vi azoy me tut

00:19:18.750 --> 00:19:22.085
un dos iz gevezn, dos lebn iz geven zeyer komplitsirt

00:19:22.429 --> 00:19:23.717
hot men gezen

00:19:23.717 --> 00:19:26.102
me ken nisht mer plats haltn.

00:19:26.142 --> 00:19:28.059
me muz dos alts likvidirn.

00:19:28.133 --> 00:19:29.713
me muz forn avek

00:19:29.787 --> 00:19:31.266
un demolt hot men

00:19:32.250 --> 00:19:35.079
hot men zikh farshtanen az me darf avekforn fun Poyln.

00:19:35.592 --> 00:19:37.251
vos ikh hob gekent, hob ikh

00:19:37.251 --> 00:19:38.522
ibergefirt

00:19:40.131 --> 00:19:42.015
un m'iz arayngeforn

00:19:42.072 --> 00:19:43.500
keyn TEL AVIV

00:19:44.586 --> 00:19:47.837
un ikh hob dortn nisht gehat keyn arbet.

00:19:48.636 --> 00:19:50.177
kh'hob gemakht a feler

00:19:50.177 --> 00:19:52.241
vos m'iz arayn in KOLKHOZ.

00:19:52.382 --> 00:19:55.430
ober fun di ale felern hot men zikh alts aroysgekopyet

00:19:55.605 --> 00:19:57.607
vayl ikh bin nokh geven yung.

00:19:57.934 --> 00:20:00.310
bin shoyn alt geven tsvey un fertsik yor

00:20:00.310 --> 00:20:02.046
⟨hob⟩ ikh nokh geven yung.

00:20:02.558 --> 00:20:04.206
hot men nokhet ongehoybn

00:20:04.802 --> 00:20:07.428
tsu dreyen, un m'hot zikh aroysgedreyt

00:20:07.570 --> 00:20:09.572
azoy lang biz kh'hob genumen

00:20:09.628 --> 00:20:12.575
geven a yor hob ikh, hob ikh gearbet, ikh hob gearbet.

00:20:12.835 --> 00:20:15.008
un di froy hot oykh tsugeholfn.

00:20:15.008 --> 00:20:16.946
m'iz aroysgan oyfn SHUK HAKARMEL.

00:20:17.020 --> 00:20:18.279
m'hot farkoyft

00:20:19.129 --> 00:20:22.008
un di tsayt fun eyn yor

00:20:22.487 --> 00:20:26.024
hot men genumen a voynung, a t- fir tsimerike voynung

00:20:26.419 --> 00:20:28.927
un m'hot dortn ayngefirt a varshtat

00:20:29.777 --> 00:20:32.656
un ikh hob genumen skhoyre, hob ikh genumen oyf komisyon

00:20:33.135 --> 00:20:34.867
in a firme KITAN

00:20:35.768 --> 00:20:37.871
iz arayngekumen der, der

00:20:39.396 --> 00:20:42.613
der MANAGER iz arayngekumen. veyst vos heyst a MANAGER?

00:20:43.648 --> 00:20:45.307
UNK zogt mit UNK

00:20:45.307 --> 00:20:47.594
di brigadir, vi azoy heyst es? MA-

00:20:46.737 --> 00:20:47.709
MANAGER

00:20:47.594 --> 00:20:48.317
MANAGER.

00:20:48.593 --> 00:20:50.932
iz arayngekumen, m'hot forgeleygt azoy.

00:20:51.124 --> 00:20:54.662
"LICHTENSTEIN, do hostu, ikh bin in a groyse firme

00:20:56.085 --> 00:20:58.087
undz vet men enk gebn skhoyre

00:20:58.414 --> 00:21:00.078
fun zuntik in di fri

00:21:00.456 --> 00:21:03.015
biz fraytik far nakhts UNK ⟨khoyv⟩.

00:21:03.426 --> 00:21:04.719
m'hot undz gegebn

00:21:04.742 --> 00:21:05.422
oyf k-

00:21:05.422 --> 00:21:06.643
oyfgezetst

00:21:06.801 --> 00:21:08.887
nor es muzts enk haltn CORRECT."

00:21:10.918 --> 00:21:12.819
yo. ikh bin maskem mit dem.

00:21:12.876 --> 00:21:14.574
m'hot ongehoybn tsu arbetn.

00:21:15.171 --> 00:21:16.447
kh'hob geshnitn

00:21:18.968 --> 00:21:21.327
vesh far, nakht vesh far froyen

00:21:21.327 --> 00:21:22.252
far kinder

00:21:23.187 --> 00:21:24.362
un

00:21:24.874 --> 00:21:26.201
m'hot gearbet.

00:21:26.528 --> 00:21:29.694
fraytik farnakht arayngetrogn ⟨dem⟩ khoyv. hot gedoyert

00:21:30.038 --> 00:21:31.382
a halb yor

00:21:31.658 --> 00:21:34.959
hot men gezogt tsu di, dortn tsu di MANAGERS

00:21:34.965 --> 00:21:36.596
eygntimer fun di

00:21:38.678 --> 00:21:40.072
fun di fabrik

00:21:40.804 --> 00:21:42.722
me darf shoyn nisht gebn keyn kredit

00:21:43.183 --> 00:21:45.202
⟨m'vet shoyn gebn⟩ ts- gelt tsu handl.

00:21:45.698 --> 00:21:47.767
yetst zog ikh az UNK

00:21:49.495 --> 00:21:51.564
oyb zey darfn gelt vel ikh UNK.

00:21:52.279 --> 00:21:53.640
azoy iz gevezn.

00:21:53.983 --> 00:21:55.242
m'hot opgehandlt

00:21:55.637 --> 00:21:59.529
vi lang bin ikh geven, fuftsn yor bin ikh gevezn sakhakl

00:21:59.670 --> 00:22:02.786
bin ikh geven efsher nayn tsen yor bin ikh geven in TEL AVIV

00:22:03.383 --> 00:22:04.828
un m'hot opgearbet

00:22:05.475 --> 00:22:06.498
un

00:22:06.859 --> 00:22:10.650
Moyshe iz demolt gevezn, hot gear- hot gelernt in

00:22:11.770 --> 00:22:13.789
GIVATAYIM hot er gelernt

00:22:14.098 --> 00:22:15.729
in tekhnikum shule

00:22:15.921 --> 00:22:17.569
tekhnik arkhitekt

00:22:19.195 --> 00:22:22.311
haklal azoy lang biz tsvontsik yor hot er gearbet

00:22:22.401 --> 00:22:23.914
hot er ge- gelernt.

00:22:24.915 --> 00:22:26.444
bay tsvontsik yor

00:22:26.586 --> 00:22:29.131
m'hot im gegat gegebn tsvey yor fray

00:22:29.131 --> 00:22:30.259
er zol endikn

00:22:30.838 --> 00:22:33.852
hot gemakht, als tekhnik hot er geendikt

00:22:34.433 --> 00:22:36.705
hot men genumen in militer oyf UNK

00:22:38.888 --> 00:22:40.485
iz er geganen in militer

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:44.096
hot er gemakht zeyer a shvern militer hot er gemakht

00:22:45.553 --> 00:22:47.794
un shpeter, m'iz gekumen tsun im

00:22:47.794 --> 00:22:49.344
er hot shoyn gedorfn endikn

00:22:50.717 --> 00:22:52.719
zol untershraybn ⟨KEVA⟩

00:22:53.755 --> 00:22:56.904
er vet zikh kenen lernen in TECHNION in, in HAIFA

00:22:57.771 --> 00:23:00.127
zogt er "ikh vil aheymforn tsu di eltern

00:23:00.420 --> 00:23:02.113
oyb zey veln mir erloybn

00:23:02.113 --> 00:23:04.127
vel ikh kumen. ikh vel untershraybn ⟨KEVA⟩.

00:23:04.875 --> 00:23:07.636
iz aheymgekumen Moyshe un zogt er azoy un azoy.

00:23:07.845 --> 00:23:09.577
"horkh" zog ikh mayn zun

00:23:09.600 --> 00:23:12.327
"ikh vel nisht mer, undz hot men nisht mer vi dikh aleynt.

00:23:13.060 --> 00:23:15.450
ikh vil nisht du zolst untershraybn ⟨KEVA⟩.

00:23:15.726 --> 00:23:19.005
du host geendikt dray UNK yor, dray yor ⟨dayn⟩ militer.

00:23:19.005 --> 00:23:19.871
genug."

00:23:20.552 --> 00:23:22.287
iz er gekumen fun militer

00:23:22.287 --> 00:23:24.377
hot ayngetsolt oyf an ekzamen

00:23:25.210 --> 00:23:28.731
un m'hot im nisht tsugelozt tsum ekzamen. m'hot gezogt s'iz shoyn nishto keyn pletser.

00:23:29.361 --> 00:23:32.105
s'iz shoyn nishto keyn pletser, hob ikh gezogt "Moyshe" zog ikh

00:23:32.314 --> 00:23:34.687
"for aher do. ⟨azoy⟩ do host a shvester

00:23:35.115 --> 00:23:36.914
un do vest ⟨dikh onheybn⟩ lernen."

00:23:37.225 --> 00:23:39.024
vu iz Moyshe geboyrn gevorn?

00:23:39.030 --> 00:23:39.980
in Poyln.

00:23:39.980 --> 00:23:40.981
in Lodzh.

00:23:41.258 --> 00:23:43.007
in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

00:23:45.207 --> 00:23:49.386
s'iz geven shver aroystsunemen keyn Yisroel fun Poyln?

00:23:49.138 --> 00:23:49.908
neyn.

00:23:50.505 --> 00:23:52.490
m'hot zikh oysgeshribn als birger

00:23:54.623 --> 00:23:57.620
oysgeshribn als birger. me fort avek keyn Yisroel

00:23:58.133 --> 00:23:59.477
un dos iz gevezn.

00:23:59.584 --> 00:24:01.839
vos m'hot gekent hot men ibergefirt

00:24:02.689 --> 00:24:04.185
un m'iz aroysgeforn.

00:24:03.448 --> 00:24:05.349
un geforn mit, mit a shif?

00:24:07.667 --> 00:24:11.356
bin geforn mit a shif, yo. m- durkh Italye zenen mir geforn.

00:24:12.038 --> 00:24:13.601
Italye zenen mir geforn.

00:24:13.506 --> 00:24:15.221
gedenkst di nomen fun shif?

00:24:14.974 --> 00:24:16.503
ver gedenkt?

00:24:17.168 --> 00:24:19.271
UNK ken ikh gedenken dem nomen fun di shif?

00:24:19.294 --> 00:24:21.009
s'iz shoyn a geshikhte vifl

00:24:21.235 --> 00:24:22.899
eyn un fertsik yor.

00:24:22.382 --> 00:24:24.316
a sakh yidn geven oyfn shif?

00:24:25.048 --> 00:24:27.624
kh'veys afilet nisht ver s'iz gevezn dortn.

00:24:33.807 --> 00:24:37.260
du bist nisht geven in militer in Po- in, in Yisroel.

00:24:37.570 --> 00:24:39.133
bin gevezn

00:24:39.139 --> 00:24:41.006
in di zeks teg milkhome

00:24:42.379 --> 00:24:43.942
bin ikh geven

00:24:44.556 --> 00:24:46.102
in HAGANA.

00:24:46.294 --> 00:24:47.672
kh'hob gehit di gasn.

00:24:48.522 --> 00:24:51.536
ven di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn, di zeks teg milkhome

00:24:52.200 --> 00:24:53.848
hob ikh mikh aleynt tsugeshtelt

00:24:54.259 --> 00:24:55.721
ikh zol akhtung gebn

00:24:56.183 --> 00:24:58.337
zol nisht zayn keyn likht in di fentster

00:24:59.085 --> 00:25:03.838
onshteln di gas, tomer iz geven likht bay di, bay di oytos, bay di CARn vos zenen geforn

00:25:03.861 --> 00:25:05.002
opgeshtelt

00:25:05.245 --> 00:25:06.285
afilet

00:25:06.409 --> 00:25:08.748
di, di POLICE ⟨iz⟩ geforn

00:25:08.856 --> 00:25:10.503
kh'hob gezen zey brenen elektrye

00:25:10.932 --> 00:25:13.761
bin ikh tsugegangen, oyfgehoybn di hant, "shtel dikh op."

00:25:13.969 --> 00:25:15.920
zol ikh vayzn UNK ⟨aza⟩ bayshpil

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:17.990
POLICE ⟨zenen geforn⟩ mit elektrye?

00:25:17.990 --> 00:25:19.239
"veys," zog ikh, "yetst

00:25:19.239 --> 00:25:20.274
iz a krig."

00:25:20.314 --> 00:25:22.957
oysgeloshn di elektrye. ikh hob gezen ⟨ergn⟩ a shtub

00:25:23.503 --> 00:25:25.218
az s'brent zikh epes

00:25:27.165 --> 00:25:30.146
⟨bin ikh⟩ geganen, geklapt di tir, "shoyn oysgeloshn.

00:25:30.220 --> 00:25:31.682
zol nisht zayn keyn shum likht."

00:25:32.143 --> 00:25:34.612
un dos iz geven in militer, vayl ikh bin shoyn geven

00:25:34.612 --> 00:25:35.681
tsu alt.

00:25:39.400 --> 00:25:40.831
dos bin ikh shoyn gevezn

00:25:40.831 --> 00:25:42.904
iber, iber fuftsik yor demolt.

00:25:43.078 --> 00:25:48.101
far di milkhome tsaytn, host, bistu, host, bistu geven in BEITAR

00:25:44.361 --> 00:25:45.300
yo

00:25:47.837 --> 00:25:48.641
yo

00:25:49.963 --> 00:25:54.530
ven bist arayn in Yisroel, hostu zikh gefilt vi in der heym?

00:25:56.157 --> 00:26:00.471
m'hot gehat mit zikh tsu tun, kh'zol krign a bisl arbet. s'iz nisht geven keyn arbet

00:26:01.202 --> 00:26:04.031
bin ikh geganen arbetn, UNK kh'hob gevoynt in RAMAT GAN.

00:26:04.645 --> 00:26:06.883
gekoyft a voynung in RAMAT GAN.

00:26:06.923 --> 00:26:08.689
keyn arbet iz nisht gevezn

00:26:08.745 --> 00:26:11.270
hot men undz gegebn, mir hot men gegebn

00:26:11.513 --> 00:26:13.416
tsvelef tog

00:26:13.416 --> 00:26:15.365
a khoydesh hot men gegebn arbet.

00:26:15.365 --> 00:26:17.211
dos hot geheysn DACHAK.

00:26:17.267 --> 00:26:18.796
veyst vos heyst DACHAK?

00:26:19.292 --> 00:26:20.470
noytik.

00:26:20.470 --> 00:26:21.970
me muz mir gebn

00:26:22.009 --> 00:26:23.235
tsvelef tog.

00:26:23.848 --> 00:26:26.677
hob ikh gearbet in MACHANE fun dem militer.

00:26:27.173 --> 00:26:29.040
kh'hob gearbet in di kikh.

00:26:29.350 --> 00:26:31.082
hob gemakht reyn.

00:26:31.122 --> 00:26:33.276
dos iz gevezn, azoy lang

00:26:33.636 --> 00:26:36.229
biz kh'hob zikh aroysgeshlept fun dortn

00:26:38.310 --> 00:26:40.531
biz UNK gan, bin gan oyf eygene hant.

00:26:41.584 --> 00:26:45.898
far vos hostu bashtimt ts- aroystsuforn fun Yisroel?

00:26:46.832 --> 00:26:48.952
tsu, nor tsulib dem

00:26:49.583 --> 00:26:52.395
vos Moyshe iz geblibn un a lerer

00:26:53.093 --> 00:26:55.249
un hot nisht gehat bay vos tsu fardinen

00:26:55.249 --> 00:26:56.950
un m'hot nisht gekent lernen

00:26:57.075 --> 00:26:58.402
vayl ikh hob gezogt

00:26:58.712 --> 00:27:01.693
az m'hot farlangt fun im, zol untershraybn ⟨KEVA⟩

00:27:02.627 --> 00:27:04.190
un ⟨zey veln im⟩ lernen

00:27:04.770 --> 00:27:07.025
in HAIFA, in TECHNION

00:27:07.133 --> 00:27:09.551
hot er mir dos gezogt. "Moyshe" zog ikh, "neyn."

00:27:09.551 --> 00:27:11.143
zog ikh "ikh hob gelt

00:27:11.200 --> 00:27:12.544
dikh tsu lernen.

00:27:12.803 --> 00:27:14.434
host geendikt dayn

00:27:14.608 --> 00:27:17.504
dayn tsayt dray yor in militer," zog ikh.

00:27:17.950 --> 00:27:19.128
"s'iz genug.

00:27:19.128 --> 00:27:20.916
ikh hob nisht mer" zog ikh "nor dikh

00:27:20.916 --> 00:27:24.491
un ikh vil du ⟨zolst dikh⟩ nisht mer lozn in militer. host opgedint.

00:27:25.206 --> 00:27:28.389
m'vet dikh nemen oyf UNK yor., azoy gut vi alemen. vest oykh geyn."

00:27:29.087 --> 00:27:31.106
nu, keyn arbet hot er nisht gehat.

00:27:32.445 --> 00:27:34.599
zog ikh "veys" zog ikh "vos?" zog ikh

00:27:34.774 --> 00:27:36.337
"for aher do azoy

00:27:36.546 --> 00:27:39.729
un do vest dikh aynordenen." do hot gevoynt di tokhter mitn eydem

00:27:40.292 --> 00:27:42.108
un er hot ongehoybn

00:27:42.267 --> 00:27:43.596
tsu tseykhenen

00:27:43.596 --> 00:27:45.669
fentster hot er ongehoybn tsu tseykhenen.

00:27:46.131 --> 00:27:49.145
ven, ven iz di tokhter aroysgeforn fun Yisroel?

00:27:49.675 --> 00:27:53.854
di tokhter iz in gantsn geven in ISRAEL, iz zi geven epes tsvey un a halb yor.

00:27:55.885 --> 00:27:58.950
un der man iz, hot, hot, vi heyst er?

00:27:58.872 --> 00:28:01.464
 er heyst BURAKEVITSH.

00:28:01.302 --> 00:28:05.143
v- un geforn iz, iz, iz oykh

00:28:05.672 --> 00:28:07.573
zey hobn zikh getrofn in Yisroel?

00:28:08.743 --> 00:28:10.807
er iz tsun ersht avekgeforn

00:28:10.807 --> 00:28:12.331
iz er avekgeforn

00:28:13.401 --> 00:28:14.880
vi hot dos geheysn?

00:28:15.426 --> 00:28:16.584
keyn BRAZIL

00:28:17.957 --> 00:28:22.659
URUGUAY. dortn iz er gevezn ⟨ergn⟩ un hot ongehoybn tsu arbetn epes in a firme

00:28:23.188 --> 00:28:25.645
un er hot zikh nisht gekent oyshaltn

00:28:25.956 --> 00:28:27.198
hot er

00:28:27.205 --> 00:28:30.911
hot er genumen a, geshribn a briv, er iz krank

00:28:31.204 --> 00:28:34.787
un der dokter hot im untergeshribn az er darf hobn a hilf

00:28:34.787 --> 00:28:36.379
er darf hobn di froy.

00:28:36.823 --> 00:28:37.942
nu, di froy ⟨er hot⟩

00:28:37.942 --> 00:28:41.829
iz aroysgeforn fun TEL AVIV, iz zi geforn dort UNK keyn BRAZIL

00:28:42.038 --> 00:28:44.631
un zenen dortn farblibn a gevise tsayt

00:28:45.092 --> 00:28:47.553
un dortn keyn gesheftn hot er oykh nisht gemakht.

00:28:47.553 --> 00:28:49.029
vos er hot gemakht hot er ge-

00:28:49.029 --> 00:28:51.009
iz alts geganen mitn kop arop

00:28:52.028 --> 00:28:53.439
un ikh hob im geshikt

00:28:53.817 --> 00:28:56.123
fun Yisroel hob ikh im geshikt a sakh gelt.

00:28:56.162 --> 00:28:57.635
kh'hob im a sakh geholfn

00:28:57.635 --> 00:28:58.974
hot er alts bagrobn

00:29:00.043 --> 00:29:01.269
azoy lang

00:29:02.001 --> 00:29:03.733
biz ikh bin do ahergekumen

00:29:04.583 --> 00:29:09.099
un ikh hob zikh ongehoybn do ayntsuordenen. s'iz mir geven zeyer, zeyer shver.

00:29:09.325 --> 00:29:11.192
ikh bin do ahergekumen, geven

00:29:11.282 --> 00:29:13.588
bin ikh alt geven efsher zeks un fuftsik yor.

00:29:13.341 --> 00:29:15.579
bist glaykh arayn in MELBOURNE arayn, yo?

00:29:16.581 --> 00:29:19.005
vayl ikh bin geforn oyf turistik.

00:29:19.821 --> 00:29:21.789
bin aroysgeforn turistik

00:29:22.572 --> 00:29:23.615
un

00:29:23.615 --> 00:29:25.671
keyn arbet hot mikh nisht gevolt tsunemen

00:29:26.082 --> 00:29:27.970
vayle me zogt ikh bin tsu alt.

00:29:28.444 --> 00:29:30.010
m'vet oyfhern di tashme yetst.
